<D>__{yeah, it's a beautiful night. i love this hot stinkin' city.}
<P>__{(pointing up park avenue)}
<D>__{... nothing else like it in the world. seven million people living on each other's heads, kids born, millionaires dying, people praying, junkies, whores, wills, lawyers, deals, parties, sex... guys like you sport dreaming about the big score. you know the best thing about new york is everything you can do here. and the worst thing is everything you can't do here...}
